short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Easy way to access grails doc.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Grails Doc extension helps you to directly go to particular grails doc using grails version from the browser address bar.

=== Usage ===

Type 'gdoc' into the browser address bar then hit tab or space to initialize the extension.
Type complete grails version eg '2.0.0' and press Enter/Return this will take you to documentation page of that particular grails version.
